WEBVTT

00:01.735 --> 00:05.239
**

00:05.273 --> 00:07.208
[ Gulls crying ]

00:07.241 --> 00:09.843
Beach!

00:09.877 --> 00:11.079
Beach!

00:11.112 --> 00:12.480
[ Crash ]

00:12.513 --> 00:13.814
Beach!

00:13.847 --> 00:15.249
[ Both gasp ]

00:15.283 --> 00:17.718
[ Sizzle ]
Beach!

00:19.187 --> 00:21.389
Beach!

00:21.422 --> 00:22.656
[ Splashing ]

00:22.690 --> 00:23.957
Beach?

00:25.559 --> 00:26.827
Beach.

00:26.860 --> 00:28.696
[ "Get Lite" by The Beatards
playing ]

00:28.729 --> 00:30.198
