* We get lifted

00:30.231 --> 00:31.765
* We get light

00:31.799 --> 00:33.334
* Hey
* We get weightless

00:33.367 --> 00:35.035
* Oh
* We satellites

00:35.069 --> 00:36.537
* We get lifted

00:36.570 --> 00:38.539
* Oh
